com.sun.identity.shared

Interface Constants

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CreateServerConfigXML, PWResetInvalidURLViewBean, PWResetQuestionModelImpl, PWResetQuestionViewBean, PWResetServlet, PWResetSuccessViewBean, PWResetUncaughtExceptionViewBean, PWResetUserValidationViewBean, PWResetViewBeanBase, Wizard

    public interface Constants
    This interface contains all the property names defined in in product configurations and may be expanded with other constant values that are used for Access and Federation Manager development.
